VALUES (65, 23, to_timestamp('2016-03-11 00:00:00.000', 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'), 'I''ve used many tablet keyboards but this one is by far the best. Fits perfectly with magnetic connection and does not come loose. The response on the keys is nice even though it is a small tablet keyboard. The fingerprint sensor was easy to setup and is accurate and easy to use. I used to use the iPad Pro with keyboard with keyboard and recently switched to a Surface with keyboard. No comparison, I was able to do so much more with the Surface.', 5, 0);
